Step 1: Open Editor & Search this "slideshow__slide slideshow__slide".

Step 2. Paste this piece of code just above it: (See Video)

        {% if block.settings.image_link != blank %}
          <a href="{{ block.settings.image_link }}">
        {% endif %}  

Step 3: Close </a>

Step 4. Search For: image_picker

Step 5. Paste this piece of code just after it (See Video)
         
          {
            "type": "url",
            "id": "image_link",
            "label": "Image Link"
          },
